'desc': [u'

Hauck Malibu Trio Set Stroller (Lolli Turquoise) Price: Rs.27900

Key Features

  • Detachable Frontbar
  • Zero Plus Comfort Car Seat
  • 4 Way Adjustable Backrest and Footrest
  • Detachable Hood
  • Large Shopping Basket
  • Lockable Front Swivel Wheels

Hauck is a German Company that has been bringing baby care products to you since 1927. The Malibu Trio Set from Hauck is complete set of baby transport system. This Malibu all in one can be used as a pram for your little ones in their first few months when they cannot sit up unaided. And once they are big enough to sit up on their own you can use the stroller.

The Malibu Stroller is made of high-quality aluminum. The entire set thus consists of the stroller
column17: a pram
column18: a zero plus car seat
column19: a handy diaper bag
column20:
a boot cover and a rain cover. The stroller had an adjustable back-rest and foot-rest to give your kid the best comfortable. The back-rest can be adjusted to four different positions to suit the baby’s comfort level.

The Malibu stroller has\xa0protective shoulder straps to keep your agile little darlings safely buckled in their seats. The detachable hood protects your baby against the harsh sun’s rays and the detachable front bar keeps your kid from falling off from the seat. This is very useful when you baby has not learnt to sit up on its own. You can remove the front bar when you do not need it.

The swivel front wheels make the stroller maneuverable and the lock on the front wheels enables you to park the stroller safely. This stroller has been innovatively designed to be quickly and compactly folded so that it fits into your car’s boot easily. The Zero Plus Comfort car seat and pram easily clips onto the adapters that are built-in the arm-rests and converts the pram to a shop and drive travel system in no time. The Zero Plus car seat will allow you to drive about on your own with your kid safely strapped into the car seat. You will not need a second person’s assistance to drive your baby to the clinic or the park.

The diaper cover will help you in packing your babies accessories like diapers
column21:
bottles and small toys. The basket in the stroller will easily hold the diaper bag or your shopping bags making your hands free to effortlessly maneuver the stroller with your baby in it.

When folded the Malibu Stroller from Hauck has the dimensions 54 x 84 x 51 cm. All the Hauck strollers and prams are made in compliance with the latest European standards.

Hauck Zero Plus Baby Car Seat (Happy World Blue) Price: Rs.7400

The Hauck Zero Plus is a car seat from Hauck that lets you travel safely with your little one. This Zero Plus Seat from Hauck has an ergonomically shaped aluminum handle that makes it easy for you to hold the seat. The extra light weight makes this Hauck Seat convenient to use. The soft padding and a centrally adjustable three-point padded seat belt keep your baby safely tucked in the car seat. Your newborn will need extra support to keep her head up and the additional head support on the Hauck Zero Plus Car Seat does exactly the same.

A strong and sturdy outer shell on the Hauck Zero Plus protects your little angel from severe impacts that could happen in a car while travelling. The easy fix system on the Zero Plus Comfort allows you to easily fix the car seat to the Malibu stroller or the Condor from Hauck. All the Hauck Car Seats are tested to conform to the latest European safety standards and the Zero Plus Comfort meets the ECE 44/04 which ensures proper safety to your tiny tot.

column16:
'desc': [u'

Hauck Roadster Stroller (Spring Red) Price: Rs.14195

Key Features

  • Front Bar has a Cup Holder to Hold the Babys Bottle
  • Five Point Safety Harness
  • Reclining Property is Operated by Pull Mechanism
  • Padded Shoulder Straps
  • Back Axle has a Suspension that Makes the Stroller Less Jerky

The Hauck\xa0Roadster SL is a three wheeled stroller and is replete with features to give maximum comfort to your precious little ones. This safety tested Roadster SL from Hauck can be used from zero months of age.

The steel frame of the Hauck Roadster imparts exceptional strength to it and makes it a reliable baby transport facility. The seat can be adjusted to fit the baby’s posture and thus the little one can comfortably sit or sleep. The reclining property is operated by a pull mechanism. The foot rest is also adjustable to reduce any discomfort to the kid. The bumper or the front bar can be adjusted to five different positions and can also be detached owing to the need. The front bar has a cup holder to hold the baby’s bottle or cup safely without toppling.

The canopy protects your kid little on from the harsh rays of the sun. The canopy and seat cover can be removed and washed easily. The fabric used in the stroller is adequately soft to give maximum comfort for you precious one. The Hauck Roadster SL has a five point safety harness with padded shoulder straps that will help in keeping your spirited angels safely buckled in their seats. A basket comes along with the Hauck Roadster which can be easily removed if not required.

The front swivel wheel that can rotate 360 degrees has a diameter of 24 cm and can be locked. The back wheels have a diameter of 29 cm each. The back axle has a suspension that makes the stroller less jerky and will give your bundle of joy a comfortable journey.

The handle on the Hauck Roadster SL can be adjusted to different heights depending on the comfort of the parent. It also has brake controls on both the sides that locks the back wheels thus
column17:
making it easy for you to control the stroller and keep your sweetheart safe all the time. All the strollers and prams from Hauck are made in compliance with the latest European standards to make sure your baby gets the best and safest products.

\n
\n ']
